room_title: Escape room "The Runic Ritual" by Two Trees Escape in Ventura
room_address: 2855 Johnson Dr Unit D Ventura, CA 93003
room_description:
You are a group of supernatural mystery solvers. You are investigating some paranormal activities deep in the woods after a string of missing person reports. 
You stumble upon a locked door at the center of an ivy labyrinth, when you turn around to get backup you discover that the maze has magically closed behind you and the only way out is to go forward, into the home of a soul stealing magician.
Your team must now collect the elemental runestones and perform the ancient Runic Ritual in order to vanquish this demonic magician.
But is there more to this magician than meets the eye? Perhaps your team will get to choose his fate in the afterlife....
